    <T n="text">0x405B7A63<!--String: "The <b>Dynasty Head</b> can start and end Alliances & Rivalries with other Dynasties. Acceptance is based on their <b>relationship</b> with the other Dynasty Head, how <b>aligned the values</b> are as well as the <b>Prestige Level</b> of both Dynasties. When an Alliance or Rivalry is formed both Dynasties will <b>gain Prestige</b>.\n\nAllied Dynasties are more successful at <b>building friendly relationships</b> and Dynasty Heads are more likely to <b>give a marriage their blessing</b>. Rival Dynasties will find it harder to build friendly relationships and may even appear looking for a fight. Being friendly with Allies or <i>unfriendly</i> with Rivals will gain Dynasty Prestige!"--></T>
